abstract: Louisiana Gov Bobby Jindal easily coasts to a second term, winning in a landslide after failing to attract any well-known or deep-pocketed opposition.
snippet: Gov. Bobby Jindal easily coasted to a second term on Saturday, winning in a landslide after failing to attract any well-known or deep-pocketed opposition.
lead_paragraph: Gov. Bobby Jindal easily coasted to a second term on Saturday, winning in a landslide after failing to attract any well-known or deep-pocketed opposition.

headline.main: Jindal Wins Second Term as Governor of Louisiana
